  "text": "Considering the results obtained for R 2 CV, R 2 V, RPD and RER, no robust equations were obtained for the prediction of VI. Similar performance was obtained by [CITATION_1] for predicting the VI of organic matter. In our study, RPD and RER were calculated as the ratio of the SECV to the s.d. or the range of the initial population, respectively.",
